summary: Try To Forget It But It Won't Stop Killing You
title: Try To Forget It But It Won't Stop Killing You
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2z6CYCf

by floralships

He nodded slowly, eyebrows still corrugated slightly. He opened his mouth, Yoongi caught sight of the synthetic tongue and teeth inside before he hesitantly snapped it shut again. He tried a few more times, seemingly searching for his voice and remembering just how to use it. Yoongi remembered that he had been pre-used before ending up with him. Had it really been that long since he was last in commission? Was he broken?

⇢ Yoongi is a lonely producer with a broken leg and an irrational fear. Hoseok is the droid that saves him.

read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2z6CYCf

by floralships

He nodded slowly, eyebrows still corrugated slightly. He opened his mouth, Yoongi caught sight of the synthetic tongue and teeth inside before he hesitantly snapped it shut again. He tried a few more times, seemingly searching for his voice and remembering just how to use it. Yoongi remembered that he had been pre-used before ending up with him. Had it really been that long since he was last in commission? Was he broken?

⇢ Yoongi is a lonely producer with a broken leg and an irrational fear. Hoseok is the droid that saves him.
